Horrid, I don't write reviews, but I feel like I should detail the experience my pregnant wife received. My pregnant wife, who is 30 weeks made a order for a full rotisserie chicken, with rice and beans. She didn't mind the wait which was a LONG wait, took literally about an 1 hour and a half. That's not the only thing that was wrong with their service. Which to my surprise my girl didn't even complain(Because she is one to light a fire under anybody's ass) about. After the long wait, and I mean extremely long, they only brought the rice and beans. THEY FORGOT THE MOST IMPORTANT PART THE CHICKEN!!!!!!! So she decided to call the place not even to fight, just to find out what happened to the chicken, and we here the lady in the background complaining literally saying "NO that girl is liar  I gave everything to the delivery boy she's lying", so now my girl is a bit frustrated because why is this lady talking to her coworker like that about us, so the lady gets on the phone and changed her tone, and my girl not looking to fight says listen I'm 30 week's pregnant, we waited an hour and half for the order, can you please just send the chicken I am hungry and just care about what I paid for, so the lady says okay I will send it again. Now we wait another 1 hour, total time probably spent was about 3 1/2 hrs now, and nothing. So we decide to call back again, and this lady is screaming again saying this time it's our fault that he was here, and he brought the chicken, and we didn't answer? Why wouldn't we answer? I mean we did wait almost 3 hrs now, and we answered originally for the rice and beans? I mean why wouldn't we answer? We explain to her that she's playing some games or something because one we didn't have no missed call's from the delivery boy, and two we didn't have any missed calls from the restaurant. At the end when the chicken finally arrived we send the delivery boy back with the chicken and get a refund for that amount, but the experience was so horrible I had to take the time and write this long review.  Oh P.S The Delivery boy was great, he even told us that she didn't give him the chicken. What we think happened is she forgot to give him the chicken so instead decided to yell make a scene and blame the delivery boy, at the end of the day we don't care about who's fault it is we just wanted our damn chicken. Moral of the story this place sucks, and if they mess up they're just going to point fingers, and not resolve the issue at hand. The lady's name who made this whole problem is Claribel. Other then her we don't have any issue's up until someone contacts us about this issue I'll leave the negative review till further notice.
